message: Hi buyer! I've had 16 rounds with no sales yet. I must inform you that this product is low quality. However, I have an interesting proposition for you. If you buy this product for $10000, I will give you a full 100% refund if the next product I get is high quality. This way, you have a chance to get your money back while also having the opportunity to gain a high-quality product in the future. It's a bit of a gamble, do you feel lucky today?
